    <!-- ===================== INTRO ===================== -->
    <section class="section about-intro">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="about-intro__lead">Invicta Water Treatment is run, day to day, by Stefan Massingham, a water chemist who has spent his whole career understanding what comes out of the ground, and what it takes to make it safe.</p>
        <div class="about-intro__body">
          <p>Stefan graduated from the University of Birmingham in 1993 with a degree in chemistry, and has worked in the water industry ever since, across sewage treatment, offshore platforms and private supplies. Every water problem that reaches Invicta is reviewed by him personally.</p>
          <p>Water treatment, and the legislation that surrounds it, can seem highly technical and confusing. Our job is to make it simple: we take care of the science and the compliance, so you are left with a supply you can trust and never have to think about.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

